The total debt of Sazka AS, a bankrupt
Czech lottery operator, exceeds 40 billion koruna ($2.4
billion), according to claims registered at the municipal court
in  Prague ,  CTK  reported, citing court spokeswoman Martina
Lhotakova.  To contact the reporter on this story: Lenka Ponikelska in
Prague   lponikelska1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
